			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				O.k to start off, there is a wiz quest in neriak.<BR>
 It starts in the casters guild from the guy in the red robe standing in the center of the main room between the pilliars (forgot his name)<BR>
 He will give you a mystical sewing kit and tell you what to do with it, then he will tell you he has the patterns for all the diffrent spurned initiate armor.(you need to ask &quot;i want to craft the spurned initiate skullcap,sleeves,sandales,gloves,bracer,robe to get the pattern)<BR>
with each pattern he will tell you the components for that item.<BR>
 then you put all of the comps in the sewing kit(not the pattern)and combine.you will get a spurned initiete cloth then you take the cloth and the pattern and put them in the sewing kit at the tailoring shop in the foreign quorter(the big white thing on the back wall)<BR>
 whoo you jest made your ferst spurned initiete armor that has ac,+1to+3int and a mana +.<BR>
<BR>
 The main component is the blood drenched cloaks that are dropped by the arcane high elfs around the pyramid in nektulos forest.(fire bolt is your best spell to get these,with a bit of trying you will find a stop by each one that you can stand and hit him with the fire bolt over and over again and he will not agro to you at all)<BR>
<BR>
 I've got all the armor but for the robe(mine is better) and its helped get my int up to 161.<BR>
<BR>
 So now you know all about it, try it im 10th lvl and had no trouble getting all the comps for each piece(the basilikes eye stalks were a pain)<BR>
<BR>
 Im still working on the last part(the final test)so i'll update this when im done good luck.<BR>
<BR>
   P.s each server has there diffrences,im in innoruk and thats haw i got the armor for wizards.<BR>

				</font>
